<h6 class="dateline">Saturday, 18 November 2023</h6>

<p><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/18/technology/sam-altman-open-ai.html">Kevin Roose, reporting for The New York Times</a>:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>An all-hands meeting for OpenAI employees on Friday afternoon 
didnâ€™t reveal much more. Ilya Sutskever, the companyâ€™s chief 
