<h2 class="dateline">Friday, 10 November 2023</h2>
<dl class="linkedlist">
<dt>
<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2023/11/10/ios-17-2-sideload-apps/">â€˜iOS 17.2 Hints at Sideloading Apps From Outside the App Storeâ€™</a>&nbsp;<a class="permalink" title="Permanent link to â€˜â€˜iOS 17.2 Hints at Sideloading Apps From Outside the App Storeâ€™â€™" href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2023/11/10/ios-17-sideloading">&#9733;</a>
