<dt>
<a href="https://mastodon.social/@gruber/111370259598983988">iOS Tip: â€˜Smart Activationâ€™ for Do Not Disturb Turns Off Notification During Screen Recordings</a>&nbsp;<a class="permalink" title="Permanent link to â€˜iOS Tip: â€˜Smart Activationâ€™ for Do Not Disturb Turns Off Notification During Screen Recordingsâ€™" href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2023/11/07/smart-activation-do-not-disturb">&#9733;</a>
