<p>Go to Settings â†’ Focus â†’ Do Not Disturb, and under â€œSet a Scheduleâ€, tap Add Schedule and enable Smart Activation. Now, when you start a screen recording, Do Not Disturb turns on automatically, and it turns itself off a few seconds after you finish recording. Iâ€™m not sure what else triggers Smart Activationâ€‰â€”â€‰the description in Settings is pretty vagueâ€‰â€”â€‰but for screen recordings this is just what I wanted.</p>

